When trying to clone from Bitbucket using Sourcetree on Win10 and it verifies the repository type, I am finding with some users on my company that they have the following error message:
{code:java}
Command: git -c diff.mnemonicprefix=false -c core.quotepath=false --no-optional-locks ls-remote https://innersource.domain.com/scm/~username/domain-test-selenium.git
Output:
Error: fatal: Authentication failed for 'https://innersource.domain.com/scm/~username/domain-test-selenium.git/'{code}
Tried using a previous version of sourcetree, but this did not work. I have been troubleshooting and looking for another solution, but cannot figure out why is this happening.

{color:#000000}"Steps to reproduce": {color}
[#open|tg://search_hashtag/?hashtag=open] [http://www.nibulon.com/data/zakupivlya-silgospprodukcii/kalkulyator-znizhok.html] 
[#select|tg://search_hashtag/?hashtag=select]{color:#000000} " Пшениця" in the field "Виберіть культуру"  {color}
[#select|tg://search_hashtag/?hashtag=select]{color:#000000} "Філія "Вознесенська"(Миколаївська область)" in the field "Базис поставки" {color}
[#enter|tg://search_hashtag/?hashtag=enter]{color:#000000} number characters ( number - 53) into index fields {color}
[#Press|tg://search_hashtag/?hashtag=Press]{color:#000000} " Розрахувати" button {color}
[#select|tg://search_hashtag/?hashtag=select]{color:#000000} " Сорго" in the field "Виберіть культуру"  {color}
[#enter|tg://search_hashtag/?hashtag=enter]{color:#000000} number characters ( number - 53) into index fields {color}
[#Press|tg://search_hashtag/?hashtag=Press]{color:#000000} " Розрахувати" button {color}
{color:#000000}"Expected Result": percentage values when  "Пшениця', "Сорго" selected {color:#000000} in the field "Виберіть культуру"  and {color}{color}{color:#000000}"Філія "Вознесенська"(Миколаївська область)" selected in the field "Базис поставки" {color}
{color:#000000}"Actual Result": {color:#172b4d}zero calculation results{color} {color:#000000}when  "Пшениця', "Сорго" selected  in the field "Виберіть культуру"  and {color}{color:#000000}"Філія "Вознесенська"(Миколаївська область)" selected in the field "Базис поставки" {color}{color}

"Steps to reproduce":
#open http://www.nibulon.com/data/zakupivlya-silgospprodukcii/kalkulyator-znizhok.html
#select " Соняшник" in the field "Виберіть культуру" 

#select "{color:#333333}Перевантажувальний термінал для перевалки зернових та олійних культур (м. Миколаїв)" in the field "{color:#b00880}Б{color:#505050}азис поставки{color}{color}"{color}
